# Mailers

## What is contained within this directory?

This directory contains the ruby code for 'mailers,' which control the sending of emails from forms on the site.

## Files contained within this directory:

### application_mailer

This is a child of the default mailer object. This isn't used by the contact forms, but is a parent of the actual contact and user mailers.

### contact_form_mailer

This is the mailer that sends the message from the contact form to the 301 Centre. 

### user_mailer

This is the mailer used by admins to email users. It can send both approve and reject emails based on the outcome of the submission 